Package: welfarebR
Title: Access Brazilian Social Assistance Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Sidney", "Bissoli", , "sbissoli76@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides functions to download and process Brazilian social
    assistance data in tidy format. Includes data from Censo SUAS (CRAS,
    CREAS, Municipal Management) and CadUnico (deidentified sample).
    Data sources are from the Ministry of Social Development (MDS).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
URL: https://github.com/sidneybissoli/welfarebR
